> <OLD>
>
> Tucson pauses to concentrate on the voices ahead.  He tries to remain unseen
> yet only visible to Big Convoy.
>
> " We're definitely not alone.  We should fall back for a moment."

The tunnel was continuing to slope downward the hum was steadily
getting more prounced. It was more of a low level vibration rather
than a true sound. Perhaps it was a machine of some sort, perhaps it
was something else.

TUSCON had just turned another corner, using the rocks and stones as
cover to keep himself out of sight when . . .

> <OLD>
>
> And underground, VICE GRIP had the pillbug DRILL BIT digging
> through, going to breka through first to be the decoy while he
> would be the muscle just up behind!

DRILL BIT's sensors were a bit off now as well. While he was somewhat
shielding by being underground and his hearing was good enough to
detect the footsteps of TUSCON as he passed by, still the ever growing
sensor distortion field was throwing off even his keen senses just a
bit.

For TUSCON he saw a CYBERTRONIAN of unknown faction rise from the
ground, bursting from the very dirt and stone! (OOC: DRILL BIT)

However unfortunately as IFF signatures were down there was no
immediate way for TUSCON to determine who he was or his factional
origin.

(TAG)

- Preston
